content.warning: Ikomi nin ɲinini in bɛ kɛ ka yamaruya caman sɔrɔ i ka telefɔni selilɛri kan, yamaruya caman bɛ faratiba la, o la, i kana u ladon walima k’u kɛ k’a sɔrɔ i ma sugu walima sɛbɛnnikɛcogo faratiw dɔn ka jɛya. Ni i ye kɔnɔkow don "Market Card Introduction" walima "Market Independent web page" sɛbɛn kɔnɔ, kɔnɔkow bɛna kɛ o yɔrɔnin bɛɛ i n'a fɔ kode. Aw ye aw janto aw yɛrɛ la.
